title: Listeners Upset With Bobby + Battle of the Bread - Red Lobster vs. Olive Garden! + 500 Push-Up Challenge Update
itunes:title: Listeners Upset With Bobby + Battle of the Bread - Red Lobster vs. Olive Garden! + 500 Push-Up Challenge Update
description:
Bobby talks about some listeners who were upset with the show for doing the International Market Challenge. We put two favorite breads head to head to determine which is better: Red Lobster’s Cheddar Bay Biscuit or Olive Garden Breadsticks. Plus, we were all challenged to do 500 push-ups in one day...we find out who actually made it through the challenge!
